is based on the strength of the unit, the race of the unit, and the type of the
equipment.  The first equip (not the basic leather on all start units) is free of cost.
Any changes after that or repairs will cost your kingdom change (typically about 1/8 to
1/3 of the cost of the unit for light to heavy armor).

The armor/weapons are actual forge equipment, but will be removed from the unit upon death
and if somehow the equipment is obtained, you cannot wear it, break it, or sell it.  The
strength of the armor/weapons depends on the unit.  It ranges from copper to mithril.  Lastly,
you can still use ores to say equip your excess steel to weaker units.

