1 LIMBS~
#Combat~
#END~
You have 4 limbs, 2 arms and 2 legs.  If you get a limb removed, you will face
certain challenges in battle (also if they are damaged, smart mobiles will target
them and break them again)

arms - If you get a limb sliced off you lose any items on that arm (gauntlets, 
weapons, shields).  You cannot use that hand to wield anything, and that slot 
is free to be attacked with no armor block bonus.

legs - If you get a leg sliced off, you lose ability to move well.  If you get
both sliced off, you cannot move at all (you either need healed, dragged to
a healer, or die to get your limbs restored).  Also, you will lose whatever greave
was on that leg.

To restore a limb you can either die (which will bring you back to 1 point of health
in all 4 limbs), goto the limb healer in Rolen camp and use the restorelimb command,
or have a cleric cast the regenlimb spell on you.

