1 MANASHELL~
#General~
#END~
Syntax:  manashell

Manashell is a powerful ability that allows you to form a protective shell around
you that will absorb any damaging magic casted against you (it will not stop
poisons or any other toxins).  Any damage spells casted against you will be
absorbed against your mana.  If you don't have enough mana, it will absorb all
the damage it can handle with your current mana. 

Like most of the skills in the Spiritual line, this is not an automatic skill,
it must be activated to use.  Once activated you will actually gain points everytime
it is used to absorb magic.
~

1 MANASHIELD~
#General~
#END~
Syntax:  manashield

Manashield acts much like the other shield lines do (ex: shockshield).  It will
put up a shield that will damage the target everytime it attempts to hit you.
This shield is a very good way to add extra damage in combat and since there is
no mana cost to activate it, it is about as close to free damage as you can
get.  Like the other skills in this sphere, you will learn this lovely skill
each time your manashield hits, so it won't take too long to get this one up.
~

1 MANASHOT~
#General~
#END~
Syntax:  manashot victim

Manashot is a powerful ability of channeling the inner energy into a blast of
energy that will cause some serious pain to the target.  Manashot works by
using mana like a spell (but it is a skill).  The damage counts as magical
damage, so enemies that are resistant/immune to it will still be able to
lessen the damage.  There is no bonus/penalities for the skill though, so
there is no mana saved for fairies or lost for ogres.

Lastly, it will autotarget your enemy if you use it in battle.
~

1 MANATAP~
#General~
#END~
