A very useful skill that allows you to collection mana and then pump it into
your mana pool pushing it over the maximum.  This allows you to have a bit of
extra mana than you would normally have (for perhaps a big battle, etc).  Once
your mana is past full it will start ticking down so it is important to use the
mana or it will be wasted. 

Eventually you will be also able to store the extra mana in jewelry that you have
added gems too (once support is coded in)
