When it comes to how intelligent a mobile is when hitting a target, it
falls into what values you set for intelligence and wisdom.  Below are the
scales and what will happen if a mob fits into it  (note they will only fit
one scale)

Int < 8 - Mobile will only target Body

Int <= 11 - Mobile will target a random body part

Int <= 14 - Mobile will target unequiped part or random body part (Also at this
            level the mobile will correctly grip a weapon)

Int <= 17 Wis < 15 - Mobile will targed unequiped limb, next target weapon limb, next
                     will target random body part.

Int <= 17 Wis > 14 - Same as above but on the random will only target a limb. 

Int <= 21 Wis < 18 - Target empty limb, then target a body part if the diff is 3 or better,
                     then target weapon limb, Lastly target random limb.

Int <= 21 Wis > 17 - Same as above but a diff of 1 or better. 

Int >= 22 wis < 22 - Target empty limb or target best possible limb to hit.

Int >= 22 wis > 21 - Target empty limb, next target a hurt limb, next target a damaged piece of 
                     equipment, lastly target best possible limb. 

