Syntax: morgue cost
Syntax: morgue newbie
Syntax: morgue quest

You can only use this command at the morgue (the healer in Rolen camp is
the current location).  This allows you to retrieve a corpse from a quest
while it is still ongoing.  This will however cost you QPS.  If you would
rather wait for your corpse to materialize at the morgue after time runs
out, you can do that and save some QPS.

Lastly, the amount of QPS increase as your Sworth does, so for a newbie
it might be only 1 QP, for a veteran it is going to cost a few more.

Recently added is the ability to get a CR from any area using the newbie
argument.  This will get all your corpses in the game and deposit them in
the room with you.  There is a rather large cost of 5 of your MAX HP, so
use this as a last ditch effort.  YOu have to have less than 100 hp and
this will only drop you down to no more than 20 HP.  If you think this
is steep you might ask a player to drag (HELP DRAG) your corpse so you
can get to it safely.

Added a bit later is the ability to get you corpse when you have more than
100 HP.  It is done using the retrieve option and costs 5% of your MAX HP.
There is a 15 minute wait before this can happen to allow anyone to loot
your corpse if they so choose (to avoid abuse).
~

