#Wilderness Mounts~
#END~
When a mount dies, it now will return to the normal recall place in
Rafermand.  You can recall to get your mount back, or simply walk back
to Rafermand and fetch it.  Also, when a mount dies its endurance is
dropped down a point or two.  So, you won't lose your mount if it dies, 
