A very useful skill that can be very useful against any enemy (note:  enemies with
massive amounts of hp have a very high resistance to this skill).  Once the nervepinch
lands, the target will attack with 1/2 the normal speed of before.  The affect is
temporary lasting a few seconds to a handful of seconds, but the attack takes very
little time to attempt (1 round) and is highly effecient in reducing damage taken
from melee.  The affects, however, are not stackable so the first neverpinch must
wear off before another one can be applied.
