A very powerful skill for those who wish to exceed in the art of combat. 
Nervestrike works a lot like stun, but think of it as a more stealth version
of it.  Nervestrike only takes 1 round of combat to attempt and when it lands
you get the same results as a stun.  The thing the sets nervestrike ahead of
stun is that enemies cannot be immune to it.  However, landing it against those
large beasts of enemies can be a difficulty feat.
~

