Power Level is the level you are assigned based on your Equipment Worth
and your Stat Worth. Since Rafermand is a levelless system numbers are
generated based on your stats. Stats are defined in this check as attribute
stats (strength, hp, mana) and also skills/spells learned.

Equipment worth is based on the strength of the equipment. Better equipment
gets assigned a higher worth. In addition, affects like hp additions, armor
additions, etc will be added to this value. Equipment worth is ONLY measured
by equipment that is worn and only checks 1 layer (so anything in a backpack
on your back is not counted).

