1 'POWER RANKING' POWER RANKING~
#General~
#END~
Power Ranking is a point value based on the quality of pkills you are making
along with your Power Level. In short, the better the person you attack, the
more Power Ranking points you will earn. The amount of points you gain is based
on the Power Ranking of the person you killed and the Power Level difference
between the two combatants. Based on these numbers you can take 0 Power Ranking
points from the other player or half of the Power Ranking points if you get a high
quality kill.

Power Ranking points are generated by your Power Level and additional points can be
earned by killing others. In general you will win this catagory by killing other people
and taking their points, but it is possible to win this catagory by stat building alone.

Lastly, the minimum Power Ranking is 1 point. You start the game with 20 and can go as
low as 1. When you reach 1 point you cannot give any points to anyone else. The winner
of a fight will get 1 point from a fight UNLESS the victim only has 1 Power Ranking Point.
~

