Syntax:  quickcombo right/left strike1 strike2 strike3 strike4 strike5 victim
Note: strike3-5 is available if you have expert/elite/flawless in quickcombo.

When it comes to dealing out pure damage in the Spiritual sphere, look no further.  
Those who completely master this skill are able to string together 5 attacks at
once and execute them in a rather quick fashion.  You start out with the ability
to string only 2 attacks together, but as your mastery increases, you gain the
next 3 attacks.

