Hide is a variety of skills combining hide, prawl, nightprawl, and lightprawl.  All 4
are in the Stealth group and gain in use/power as you go up.  Hide is the most basic
version that allows you to hide anywhere as long as it is nighttime.  However, you cannot
move with just the hide skill (note fairies can hide natually with no knowledge of the
skill).  The next step up, prawl, allows you to move while hidden as long as it is night
and the sector isn't a road/path.  The next skill up (nightprawl) allows free movement
at night and lightprawl allows free movement in the light.

