1 TRADEGOODS~
#Kingdoms Management~
#END~
-----------------------Below are for trading between kingdoms-----------------------
Syntax: tradegoods list.
Syntax: tradegoods set <number> <item> <offer/want> <value>.
Syntax: tradegoods start <kingdon name/number>.
Syntax: tradegoods send <number>.
