show uid       - Shows only the uid you specify (uid is Unique ID)
show area name - Shows only the resets in a certain area (must specify filename of area not
                 the actual area name)
show all       - Shows all traps that exist in the game.
show reset     - Shows all traps that exist as a reset.
show inv       - Shows all traps that exist in the inventory of players.
show loaded    - Shows all traps that are loaded on an object.
show noloaded  - Shows all traps that are not loaded on an object.
show frag      - Shows all traps with a frag setting of 1 or greater.
