#Kingdoms~
#Kingdoms Military~
#END~
Units are anything you purchase with buycaste mobs.  A unit is typically a military unit
under which you can control using command and giveorders.  Also included in this general
term are worker units (HELP WORKERUNIT).  You don't have as much control over these units,
but they generall just extract resources anyway.

